{
    "poem_title": "Gâté",
    "author": "Germain Nouveau",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1922",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Comme une femme, hélas ! vous change !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi, moi… je fume toujours,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Je ris, je dors, je bois, et mange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Mais tu m’as rendu bien étrange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Et de tous les fils, le plus lourd.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Comme une femme, hélas ! vous change !\nAinsi, moi… je fume toujours,\nJe ris, je dors, je bois, et mange,\nMais tu m’as rendu bien étrange,\nEt de tous les fils, le plus lourd."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Un fils qui foule au pied sa mère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ce que le dernier des troupiers",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Au pas accéléré peut faire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Qui s’oublie, ô folie amère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu’à l’écraser sous ses pieds !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un fils qui foule au pied sa mère,\nCe que le dernier des troupiers\nAu pas accéléré peut faire,\nQui s’oublie, ô folie amère,\nJusqu’à l’écraser sous ses pieds !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Eh ! oui, je foule aux pieds la Terre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Qu’à deux genoux a su baiser",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Un Romain plein d’amour sévère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Brutus, que j’appelle mon frère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "J’ai pu quelquefois l’écraser.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh ! oui, je foule aux pieds la Terre\nQu’à deux genoux a su baiser\nUn Romain plein d’amour sévère,\nBrutus, que j’appelle mon frère,\nJ’ai pu quelquefois l’écraser."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Écraser qui ? la Terre où l’homme ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Les deux, n’en soyons pas surpris :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Le Temps est le grand agronome ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Il peut aux poussières de Rome",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Mêler les cendres de Paris.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Écraser qui ? la Terre où l’homme ?\nLes deux, n’en soyons pas surpris :\nLe Temps est le grand agronome ;\nIl peut aux poussières de Rome\nMêler les cendres de Paris."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Oui, la Terre en travail et soûle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Notre Mère à tous, n’est-ce pas ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Mère des fous et de la foule,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Et dont on mange, je la foule",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Amoureusement sous mes pas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oui, la Terre en travail et soûle,\nNotre Mère à tous, n’est-ce pas ?\nMère des fous et de la foule,\nEt dont on mange, je la foule\nAmoureusement sous mes pas."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Car cette Mère elle ne gronde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Jamais ses fils, et nous avons",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Son sang qui circule à la ronde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Le vin rose et la bière blonde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Dans les verres où nous buvons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Car cette Mère elle ne gronde\nJamais ses fils, et nous avons\nSon sang qui circule à la ronde,\nLe vin rose et la bière blonde\nDans les verres où nous buvons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Quant à la vraie ou bien la fausse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Nous dirons comme nous voudrons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Elle est morte, elle est dans sa fosse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Je n’en pleure ni ne m’en gausse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Dans la fosse où nous pourrirons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quant à la vraie ou bien la fausse,\nNous dirons comme nous voudrons,\nElle est morte, elle est dans sa fosse,\nJe n’en pleure ni ne m’en gausse\nDans la fosse où nous pourrirons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "C’était une enfant de Pourrières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Village battu des grands vents,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Où toutes peuvent passer, fières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "De leurs magnifiques derrières",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Aussi crânes que leurs devants.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’était une enfant de Pourrières,\nVillage battu des grands vents,\nOù toutes peuvent passer, fières,\nDe leurs magnifiques derrières\nAussi crânes que leurs devants."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Elle m’adorait pas des flottes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "C’est loin comme les fonds usés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Les premiers fonds de mes culottes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Elle m’a foutu deux… calottes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Elle qui comptait les baisers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle m’adorait pas des flottes !\nC’est loin comme les fonds usés,\nLes premiers fonds de mes culottes.\nElle m’a foutu deux… calottes\nElle qui comptait les baisers."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Et pourquoi ? Tenez, je m’essuie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Encore, en vous le racontant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "(Je cesserai si ça t’ennuie),",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "C’est parce qu’un beau jour de pluie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "J’étais revenu « tout coulant ».",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et pourquoi ? Tenez, je m’essuie\nEncore, en vous le racontant\n(Je cesserai si ça t’ennuie),\nC’est parce qu’un beau jour de pluie\nJ’étais revenu « tout coulant »."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Encor si c’était la férule !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Mais la main sur la joue, ah ! non !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Bon pour un homme, s’il recule.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "L’autre au moins, c’est chaud, ça vous brûle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Pas bien loin du… petit couillon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Encor si c’était la férule !\nMais la main sur la joue, ah ! non !\nBon pour un homme, s’il recule.\nL’autre au moins, c’est chaud, ça vous brûle\nPas bien loin du… petit couillon."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Elle s’appelait Augustine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Silvy, beau nom, grand et gaillard,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "D’une source, on dirait, latine ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Elle est morte de la poitrine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Malgré tous les secours de l’art.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle s’appelait Augustine\nSilvy, beau nom, grand et gaillard,\nD’une source, on dirait, latine ;\nElle est morte de la poitrine\nMalgré tous les secours de l’art."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Elle était charmante et divine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Comme l’aveugle et le vieillard.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Je sais que sa jambe était fine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Je trouve un jour ses bas, ma fine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Je les mis… pour l’amour de l’art.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle était charmante et divine,\nComme l’aveugle et le vieillard.\nJe sais que sa jambe était fine,\nJe trouve un jour ses bas, ma fine,\nJe les mis… pour l’amour de l’art."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Elle me lisait quoi ? devine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Les vers du Petit Savoyard !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
