                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Ma mère (oh ! c’est rempli d’art)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Elle me lisait quoi ? devine\nLes vers du Petit Savoyard !\nAutant mourir de la poitrine.\nC’est dans ces vers que se dessine\nMa mère (oh ! c’est rempli d’art)"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Qui dit, nom de Dieu de mâtine !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Va-t’en à son enfant qui part !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Autant mourir de la poitrine !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Ce qu’elle fit. J’usai sa mine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "De bas noirs, pour l’amour de l’art.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qui dit, nom de Dieu de mâtine !\nVa-t’en à son enfant qui part !\nAutant mourir de la poitrine !\nCe qu’elle fit. J’usai sa mine\nDe bas noirs, pour l’amour de l’art."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 16,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Elle n’avait, ma Valentine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Pas le quart de ton cœur… le quart !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
